Package: nhschooldata
Title: Fetch and Process New Hampshire School Enrollment Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Al", "Martin", , "almartin@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Downloads and processes school enrollment data from the New Hampshire
    Department of Education (NH DOE). Provides functions for fetching enrollment
    data from the iPlatform reporting system and NCES Common Core of Data,
    transforming it into tidy format for analysis. Supports historical data
    from 2006 to present.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
